# Example of custom action message
# structure is Goal --- Result --- Feedback
#
# This can include simple data types like int or bool
# Alternatively, standard message types like geometry_msgs/msg/Twist can be used


# Goal - what the client sends to request the action
int32 target_count
---
# Result - final outcome sent when action completes
bool success
string message
int32 final_count
---
# Feedback - periodic updates during action execution
int32 current_count
float32 percent_complete